node.text: Celebrate the last week of Hispanic Heritage Month with National Mixologist @janedangersays and the elevated flavors of the Batanga. This creative cocktail proves that the boldest flavors are never forgotten- and is easy enough to create at home 🍹 #TequilaElevated

node.text: Hispanic Heritage Month is starting on an elevated note as our National Mixologist @janedangersays celebrates the influence and flavors of the Chelada and the Michelada. With tips, history, and hacks you can easily mix along with Jane, or save for your next happy hour 🍹 #TequilaElevated

For us, the Rosarita is an invitation to rethink  everything you know about Tequila and Rosé. A smooth elevated cocktail that will put a smile on your face.
